	function BindHotKeys(strJSON) {
		if (strJSON.length > 0) {
			var hotkey = JSON.parse(strJSON);

			if ($.type(hotkey) == "object") {
				// unbind first
				$(document).unbind("keydown");

				$(document).on("keydown", function (e) {
					
					 //in case users use keypad
					if (e.altKey && e.ctrlKey) {
						e.which = SwapHotKeys(e, hotkey);
					}


					// new classes for hotkeys
					if (e.altKey && e.ctrlKey && (e.which == hotkey.SearchWindowKeyValue)) {
						// 05/16/2016 HB -- bring up the nav if it's insible then show the search
						if ($("div.divNavTreeWrapperClass").attr("style") != undefined) {
							if ($("div.divNavTreeWrapperClass").attr("style").indexOf("none;") >= 0) {
								$("div.divNavTreeWrapperClass").velocity("slideDown", {
									duration: 250,
									complete: function () {
										$(".submit-student-search-sidebar").click();
									}
								});
							}
							else {
								// bring up the stu search
								$(".submit-student-search-sidebar").click();
							}
						}
						else {
							// bring up the stu search
							$(".submit-student-search-sidebar").click();
						}
					}
					else if (e.altKey && e.ctrlKey && (e.which == hotkey.NextStudentKeyValue)) {
						// next stu
						__doPostBack('ctl00$btnNext', '');
					}
					else if (e.altKey && e.ctrlKey && (e.which == hotkey.PreviousStudentKeyValue)) {
						// previous stu
						__doPostBack('ctl00$btnPrevious', '');
					}
					else if (e.altKey && e.ctrlKey && (e.which == hotkey.FirstStudentKeyValue)) {
						// first stu
						$(".nav-tree-student-search-wrapper input[id$='btnFirst']").click();
					}
					else if (e.altKey && e.ctrlKey && (e.which == hotkey.LastStudentKeyValue)) {
						// previous stu
						$(".nav-tree-student-search-wrapper input[id$='btnLast']").click();
					}
					else {
						// do nothing
					}

				});
			}
		}
	}

	function SwapHotKeys(e, hotkeys) {
		if((e.which >= 96) && (e.which <= 106)) {
			if (((parseInt(hotkeys.SearchWindowKeyValue) >= 48) && (parseInt(hotkeys.SearchWindowKeyValue) <= 57)) ||
				((parseInt(hotkeys.PreviousStudentKeyValue) >= 48) && (parseInt(hotkeys.PreviousStudentKeyValue) <= 57)) ||
				((parseInt(hotkeys.FirstStudentKeyValue) >= 48) && (parseInt(hotkeys.FirstStudentKeyValue) <= 57)) ||
				((parseInt(hotkeys.LastStudentKeyValue) >= 48) && (parseInt(hotkeys.LastStudentKeyValue) <= 57))) {

				return e.which - 48
			}
		}
		if ((e.which >= 48) && (e.which <= 57)) {
			if (((parseInt(hotkeys.SearchWindowKeyValue) >= 96) && (parseInt(hotkeys.SearchWindowKeyValue) <= 105)) ||
				((parseInt(hotkeys.PreviousStudentKeyValue) >= 96) && (parseInt(hotkeys.PreviousStudentKeyValue) <= 105)) ||
				((parseInt(hotkeys.FirstStudentKeyValue) >= 96) && (parseInt(hotkeys.FirstStudentKeyValue) <= 105)) ||
				((parseInt(hotkeys.LastStudentKeyValue) >= 96) && (parseInt(hotkeys.LastStudentKeyValue) <= 105))) {

				return e.which + 48
			}
		}

		return e.which;
	}

	var userHasScrolled = 0;

	function ScrollNav() {
		if (NavScrolled == false) {		
			// Scroll Nav nicely.		
			try {
				if (userHasScrolled == 0) {
					var scrolltome = "";
					// Pages
					if ($("#all-pages-submit").find(".sidebar-quick-access-icon-on").is(":visible")) {
						scrolltome = ".selected-link-wrapper";
						// Reports
					} else if ($("#reports-submit").find(".sidebar-quick-access-icon-on").is(":visible")) {
						scrolltome = ".reports-root-link.Selected";
					}
					if (scrolltome != "" && $(scrolltome).length > 0) {
						$(scrolltome).velocity("scroll", {
							container: $("#sidebar-content"), duration: 250, offset: -250,
							complete: function () {
								var scrollToThis = $("#sidebar-content").scrollTop();
								$("#sidebar-content").slimScroll({ scrollTo: scrollToThis + "px" });
								NavScrolled = true;
							}
						});
					} else {
						$("#sidebar-content").slimScroll({ scrollTo: "0px" });
					}
				}				
			} catch (Err) {
			}
		}
	}

	function ScrollNavToHighlight() {
		setTimeout(function () {
			try {
				var highlightedtoppx = $('.NavHighlighted').offset().top + $("#sidebar-content").scrollTop();
				var scrolltopx = $('.NavHighlighted').offset().top;
				if (scrolltopx < 0) { scrolltopx = 0; }
				scrolltopx = (scrolltopx - $("#sidebar-content").offset().top);
				if (scrolltopx < 0) { scrolltopx = 0; }

				var topsee = $("#sidebar-content").scrollTop() + $("#sidebar-content").offset().top;
				var bottomsee = ($("#sidebar-content").height() + $("#sidebar-content").scrollTop() + $("#sidebar-content").offset().top);
				if (topsee > highlightedtoppx || bottomsee < highlightedtoppx) {
					$("#sidebar-content").slimScroll({ scrollTo: scrolltopx + "px" });
				}
			} catch (ex) {}		
		}, 20);		
	}

		// Clicking on the Scrollbar makes it stay around.

		$('body').on("change paste blur focus", ".student-search-pop-input", function () {

			if (localStorage.getItem("LoginCheck") === "true" && window.location.origin != 'https://demo.aeries.net') {
				UserAccountOptionsService.GetOption("DarkMode", (state) => {
					localStorage.setItem("DarkMode", state.toLowerCase());
				});

            } else if (window.location.origin === 'https://demo.aeries.net') {
				localStorage.removeItem('DarkMode');
                localStorage.setItem("LoginCheck", "false");
            }
		} catch (ex) {

		let DefaultStudentSearchLimit = 250;
		GeneralFunctions.SetSearchResultLimit(DefaultStudentSearchLimit);
	});

	function ToggleSuggestion() {
		try {
			var searchterm = $(".student-search-pop-input").val();

			if (searchterm.length >= 20 && ((searchterm.match(new RegExp(",", "g")) || []).length >= 2 || (searchterm.match(new RegExp(" ", "g")) || []).length >= 5 || (searchterm.match(new RegExp("	", "g")) || []).length >= 2)) {
				$(".suggest-actions").show();
			} else {
				$(".suggest-actions").hide();				
			}
		} catch(Ex) {
		}
	}

			} else {
				newlocation = newlocation + "&changedstu=true";
			}
			window.location = newlocation;
		}, 200);
	}

	function CurrentURL() {
		var thisCurrentURL = window.location.pathname.substr(window.location.pathname.lastIndexOf("/") + 1) + window.location.search;
		// Get currently selected TreeNode Element
		if ($("a.TreeNodeSelected").length > 0) {
			thisCurrentURL = $("a.TreeNodeSelected").first().attr('href');
		} else {
			// Find in Report list
			var currentPageTitle = CurrentPageTitle();
			var URLfound = 0;
			$("a[id*='_lnkReport'] span:contains('" + currentPageTitle + "')").each(function () {
				// Exact name, not just contains.
				if ($.trim($(this).text()) == currentPageTitle) {
					thisCurrentURL = $(this).closest("a").attr("href");
					URLfound = 1;
				}
			});
			// Not selected in nav, but there.
			if (URLfound === 0) {
				$("a.sidebar-link[title='" + currentPageTitle + "']").each(function () {
					if (URLfound === 0) {
						thisCurrentURL = $(this).attr("href");
						URLfound = 1;
					}
				});
			}
		}
		return $.trim("~/" + thisCurrentURL);
	}

	function CurrentPageTitle() {
		var thisCurrentPageTitle = 'Aeries';
		if ($(document).find("title").length > 0) {
			thisCurrentPageTitle = $.trim($(document).find("title").text());
		}
		if ($(".page-title").length > 0) {
			thisCurrentPageTitle = $.trim($(".page-title").first().text());
		}
		
		// Find Report
    	var thispage = window.location.pathname.substr(window.location.pathname.lastIndexOf("/") + 1) + window.location.search;
    	if ($("#reports-base-list a[href$='" + thispage + "'] span").length > 0) {
    		// Find exact match, fall back if not.
    		if ($("#reports-base-list a[href='" + thispage + "'] span").length > 0) {
    			thisCurrentPageTitle = $("#reports-base-list a[href='" + thispage + "'] span").first().text();
    		} else {
    			thisCurrentPageTitle = $("#reports-base-list a[href$='" + thispage + "'] span").first().text();
    	}
    	}
    	if ($(".reports-root-link.Selected span:not(.metadata)").length === 1) {
    		thisCurrentPageTitle = $(".reports-root-link.Selected span:not(.metadata)").text().trim();
    	}

		// Get currently selected TreeNode Element
		if ($("a.TreeNodeSelected").length > 0) {
			thisCurrentPageTitle = $("a.TreeNodeSelected").first().attr('title');
			// Remove () from name
			try {
				thisCurrentPageTitle = thisCurrentPageTitle.split("(")[0];
			} catch (Err) {
			}			
		}
		return $.trim(thisCurrentPageTitle);
	}

	function AddFavorite() {
		var currentPageTitle = CurrentPageTitle();
		var currentURL = CurrentURL();

		UserAccountOptionsService.AddFavorite(currentURL, currentPageTitle, DoNothing);

		// Add Element to the dom
		var html = '<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="border-width:0;" class="sidebar-link-wrapper Clickable zebra">';
		html = html + '<tbody><tr><td><div style="width:5px;height:1px"></div></td>';
		html = html + '<td><img src="images/blank.gif" alt=""></td><td class="TreeNode LeafNode sidebar-link" onmouseover="TreeView_HoverNode(ctl00_NavigationTree_Data, this)" onmouseout="TreeView_UnhoverNode(this)"><a class="TreeNode LeafNode sidebar-link" href="' + currentURL.replace("~/","") + '" style="border-style:none;font-size:1em;">' + currentPageTitle + '</a></td>';
		html = html + '</tr></tbody></table>';
		$("#ctl00_NavigationTreen1Nodes").append(html);

		var trhtml = '<tr><td class="Data" align="center">';
		var trhtml = trhtml + '<a onclick="if(window.confirm(\'Are you sure  you want to remove this favorite?\')) RemoveFavorite(\'' + currentPageTitle + '\'); return false;" id="new_btnRemoveFavorite" href="javascript:void()"><span class="fa fa-close aeries-red"></span></a>';
		var trhtml = trhtml + '</td><td class="Data"><a href="' + currentURL.replace("~/", "") + '" target="_self">' + currentPageTitle + '</a></td></tr>';
		$("#ctl00_gvFavorites tbody").append(trhtml);
		// Prevent Default
		return false;
	}

	function RemoveFavorite(pageTitle) {
		// Pass in, or current page
		if (!pageTitle) {
			pageTitle = CurrentPageTitle();
		}		
		UserAccountOptionsService.RemoveFavorite(pageTitle, DoNothing);

		// Remove Element from the dom - Edit Favorite
		$("#ctl00_Favorite_Panel a:contains('" + pageTitle + "')").each(function () {
			// Exact name, not just contains.
			if ($.trim($(this).text()) == pageTitle) {
				// Remove the "<tr>" for the whole row.
				$(this).closest("tr").remove();
			}
		});

		// Remove Element from the dom - Favorite List
		$("#ctl00_NavigationTreen1Nodes a:contains('" + pageTitle + "')").each(function () {
			// Exact name, not just contains.
			if ($.trim($(this).text()) == pageTitle) {
				// Remove the "<tr>" for the whole row.
				$(this).closest("table").remove();
			}
		});

		// Prevent Default
		return false;
	}

    // Cancel Editing Favorites
	function CancelEditFavorite() {
		$("#favorites-submit").click();
	}

	function OpenPopup() {
		$find('pceFavorites').showPopup();
	}

	function ChangeSchoolAndSetStudentConfirm(result, options) {

		if (result) {
			ChangeSchoolAndSetStudentFromOptionsObject(options);
		}
	}

	function StudentSearchDoNotWarnChangeSchool(options) {
		UserAccountOptionsService.SetOption('StudentSearch_DoNotWarnChangeSchool', 'True', DoNothing);
		aeriesWin.prototype.alert('We will not ask you again. You can change this preference on the Account Settings page.', ChangeSchoolAndSetStudentConfirm, options);
	}

<script>

	function redflagWidth() {
		try {
			// Detect if one line comment and needs hover
			if ($('.page-flag-comment').outerWidth() <= 280 && $('.page-flag-datetime').text().length == 0 ) {
				$('.page-flag-comment-details').addClass('one-line');
				$('.page-flag-comment').addClass('one-line');
			} else {
				$('.page-flag-comment-details').removeClass('one-line');
				$('.page-flag-comment').removeClass('one-line');
			}
		} catch (ex) {
		}		
	}

	function CallPrintFromTitle(jQuerySelectQuery) {
		if (typeof jQuerySelectQuery !== 'undefined') {
			try {
				if ($(jQuerySelectQuery).first().is(":visible")) {
					if ($(jQuerySelectQuery).first().is("a")) {
						if ($(jQuerySelectQuery).first().prop("href").startsWith("javascript")) {
							eval($(jQuerySelectQuery).first().prop("href"));
						}
						else {
                            $(jQuerySelectQuery).first().click();
							if (typeof $(jQuerySelectQuery).first().prop("target") !== 'undefined') {
                                 window.open($(jQuerySelectQuery).first().prop("href"), $(jQuerySelectQuery).first().prop("target"));
							} else {
								$(jQuerySelectQuery).first().click();
							}							
						}
					}
					else {
						if (typeof $(jQuerySelectQuery).first().attr('onclick') !== 'undefined' && $(jQuerySelectQuery).first().attr('onclick').length >= 1) {
							eval($(jQuerySelectQuery).first().attr("onclick").toString().replace('return false;', ''));
						} else {
							$(jQuerySelectQuery).first().click();
						}						
					}
				}
			} catch (err) {
				log(3, "Could not Print. " + err);
			}
		} else {
			// if we find the existing print button, use it's functionality, otherwise fall back to default print page or give error / hide button.
			if ($("#PrintTestResults").length >= 1) {
				$("#PrintTestResults").click();
			} else {
				if ($("input[value='Print']:visible").length >= 1) {
					$("input[value='Print']:visible").first().click();
				} else if ($("input[id*='btnRunReport']:visible").length >= 1) {
					$("input[id*='btnRunReport']:visible").first().click();
				} else {
					if ($("input[id*='btnPrint']").length >= 1) {
						if ($("input[id*='btnPrint']:visible").length >= 1) {
							$("input[id*='btnPrint']:visible").first().click();
						} else {
							$("input[id*='btnPrint']").first().click();
						}
					} else {
						window.print();
					}
				}
			}
		}
	}
		
	var PrintLines = [];

	function showOrHidePrintButton() {

		$("#print-submit").hide();
		$("#multi-print").hide();
		PrintLines = [];

		var selectors = ".mainprint";

		if (selectors.indexOf("(") >= 1) {

			$("#print-submit").show();

		} else {

			$(selectors).each(function () {
				if ($(this).is(":visible") || $(this).hasClass("hiddenPrintRpt")) {
					var thisSelector = '';
					var id = $(this).attr("id");
					if (id) {
						thisSelector = "#" + id;
					} else {
						var classNames = $(this).attr("class");
						if (classNames) {
						  thisSelector = "." + $.trim(classNames).replace(/\s/gi, ".") + ":visible";
						}
					}
					if (thisSelector) {
						PrintLines.push(thisSelector);
					}
				}
			});

			if (PrintLines.length >= 2) {
				$("#multi-print-ul").html("");
				PrintLines.forEach(function (PrintLineSelector) {
					var PrintLine = $(PrintLineSelector).first();
					var PrintLineText = PrintLine.text().trim();
					try {
						if (PrintLineText.length <= 0) {
						PrintLineText = PrintLine.val().trim();
						}
						if (PrintLineText.length <= 0) {
							PrintLineText = "Print";
						}
					} catch (ex) {
					}
					
					$("#multi-print-ul").append('<li class="zebra"><a href="#" onclick="CallPrintFromTitle(\'' + PrintLineSelector + '\')">' + PrintLineText + '</a></li>');
				});

				$("#multi-print").show();

			} else if(PrintLines.length == 1) {
				$("#print-submit").show();
			}

		}
		
		
	}

	(function () {

		redflagWidth();

		

		setTimeout(function () {
			showOrHidePrintButton();
		}, 100);

		$(window).load(function () {
			setTimeout(function () {
				showOrHidePrintButton();
			}, 100);
			setTimeout(function () {
				showOrHidePrintButton();
			}, 800);
			setTimeout(function () {
				showOrHidePrintButton();
			}, 2100);
			setTimeout(function () {
				showOrHidePrintButton();
			}, 8200);

			
		});
		
		
		$("#print-submit").click(function () {
			
			CallPrintFromTitle(".mainprint");
			
		});

		$("#page-tour").click(function () {
			
		});

		$("#StartTourWelcomeYes").click(function () {

			var dialogStartTour = $("#StartTourWelcome").data("kendoWindow");
			setTimeout(function () {
				dialogStartTour.close();
			}, 1);

			// Start Tour
			setTimeout(function () {
				$("#page-tour").click();
			}, 10);
		});

		$("#StartTourWelcomeNo").click(function () {
			var dialogStartTour = $("#StartTourWelcome").data("kendoWindow");
			setTimeout(function () {
				dialogStartTour.close();
			}, 1);


			setTimeout(function () {
				var replayTour = new Tour({
					name: "tour_PlayTour",
					backdrop: true,
					storage: false,
					template: '<div class="popover" role="tooltip"> <div class="arrow"></div> <h3 class="popover-title"></h3> <div class="popover-content"></div> <div class="popover-navigation"> <div class="btn-group" style="display:none;"> <button class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-role="prev" style="font-size: 14px;">&laquo; Prev</button> <button class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-role="next" style="font-size: 14px;">Next &raquo;</button> <button class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-role="pause-resume" data-pause-text="Pause" data-resume-text="Resume" style="font-size: 14px;">Pause</button> </div> <button class="btn btn-sm btn-default" data-role="end" style="font-size: 14px; width:100%;">OK</button> </div> </div>',
					onStart: function (tour) {
						$(".page-options-dropdown").addClass('AlwaysShow');
					},
					steps: [					
						{
							element: ".page-options-dropdown",
							title: "Play Tour",
							placement: "bottom",
							content: 'Play this tour any time by clicking<br><i class="fa fa-ellipsis-v" aria-hidden="true"></i> then <i class="fa fa-play-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i> Page Tour.'
						},
						{
							element: ".page-options-dropdown",
							title: "Play Tour",
							placement: "bottom",
							content: 'Play this tour any time by clicking <br><i class="fa fa-play-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i> Page Tour.'
						}
					],
					onEnd: function (tour) {
						setTimeout(function () {
							if ($(".page-options-dropdown").hasClass('AlwaysShow')) {
								$(".page-options-dropdown").removeClass('AlwaysShow');
							}
						}, 10);
					}
				});

				StartTour(replayTour);
			}, 100);
		});


		

		var hasFlag = $(".page-flag").hasClass("flagged");
		if (hasFlag == true) {
			$(".page-option-default.fa-flag-o").removeClass("fa-flag-o").addClass("fa-flag");
			$(".page-option-readonly.fa-flag-o").removeClass("fa-flag-o").addClass("fa-flag");
		}

		
	})();
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
	function PreviousStudent() {
		try {
			var $toClick = $('.active-student').prev("a").length > 0 ? $('.active-student').prev("a") : $('.namelist a').last();
			window.location = $toClick.attr('href');
		} catch (Err) {
		}
	}
	function NextStudent() {
		try {
			var $toClick = $('.active-student').next("a").length > 0 ? $('.active-student').next("a") : $('.namelist a').first();
			window.location = $toClick.attr('href');
		} catch (Err) {
		}
	}

	var localStorageprefix = 'SubStuTopAll';

	$(document).ready(function () {

		var bodyIsCollapsed = localStorage.getItem(localStorageprefix + "IsCollapsed");
		

		$("#stu-top-all-loader").hide();
		
		if (bodyIsCollapsed == 'true') {
			if ($("#stu-top-all-collapse").hasClass('icon-expanded')) {
				setTimeout(function () {
					$("#stu-top-all-collapse").click();
				}, 0);
			}
		} else {			
			var tabSelection = localStorage.getItem(localStorageprefix + "TabSelection");
			if (tabSelection) {
				$(".tab" + tabSelection + "Label > a").click();
			}			
			$("#stu-top-all-body").velocity("fadeIn", { duration: 150 });
		}

		toggleTabBottomBorder(bodyIsCollapsed);

		$("img.student-flag-image").show();
		$("img.student-flag-image").closest("table").addClass("aeries-background-red-light");
		
	});

	// Remember tab selection
	$(".tab-label").on("click", function () {
		localStorage.setItem(localStorageprefix + "TabSelection", $(this).attr("rel"));
		var bodyIsCollapsed = localStorage.getItem(localStorageprefix + "IsCollapsed");

		if (bodyIsCollapsed == 'true' || $("#stu-top-all-collapse").hasClass("icon-collapsed")) {			
			$("#stu-top-all-body").velocity("slideDown", { duration: 150, complete: function () { EasyRePaint(); } });
			$("#stu-top-all-collapse").removeClass('icon-collapsed').addClass('icon-expanded');
			$("#stu-top-all-collapse").attr('title', 'Click to Collapse');
			localStorage.setItem(localStorageprefix + "IsCollapsed", false);
		}
		setTimeout(function () {
			EasyRePaint();
		},10);
	}, 10);

	$("#stu-top-all-collapse").on("click", function () {
		var isCollapsed = $(this).hasClass('icon-expanded');
		localStorage.setItem(localStorageprefix + "IsCollapsed", isCollapsed);
		toggleTabBottomBorder(isCollapsed.toString());
	});

	function toggleTabBottomBorder(bodyIsCollapsed) {

		var activeTab = $(".widget-options ul.nav-tabs li.active");

		if (bodyIsCollapsed == 'true') {
			activeTab.removeClass('active');
		} else {
			var tabSelection = localStorage.getItem(localStorageprefix + "TabSelection");
			if (tabSelection) {
				if ($(".tab" + tabSelection + "Label").length > 0) {
					$(".tab" + tabSelection + "Label > a").click();
					$(".tab" + tabSelection + "Label").addClass("active");
				} else {
					$("#sub-stu-top-all li a:visible").first().click();
				}
			}
		}
	}


</script>

}, 10);

	function GetIndicatorsLegend() {
		$.ajax({
			type: "GET",
			url: "Transcripts/TranscriptIndicatorMappers/GetTranscriptIndicators",
			cache: false,
			success: function (response) {
				if (response && response.length) {
					var legend = '';
					$.each(response, function (i, obj) {
						if (!legend.includes(obj.Code + " = " + obj.Description)) {
							legend += (legend ? "; " : "") + obj.Code + " = " + obj.Description;
						}
					});
					$(".CourseHistory").find("td[id*='indicatorsLegend']").html(legend);
				}
			},
			error: function (error) {
				console.log(error);
			}
		});
	};

	function GetMappedIndicators() {
		$.ajax({
			type: "GET",
			url: "Transcripts/TranscriptIndicatorMappers/GetMappedIndicators",
			data: getTranscriptParams(),
			cache: false,
			success: function (response) {
				if (response) {
					INDICATOR_CACHE = response;
					$("tr[id*='ReadRow1']").each(function (i, row) {
						var key = i + "_" + CURRENT_STUDENT_ID;
						if (INDICATOR_CACHE[key]) {
							$(this).find("td[id*='indicatorsRead']").html(INDICATOR_CACHE[key]);
						}
					});
				}
			},
			error: function (error) {
				console.log(error);
			}
		});

	function getTranscriptParams() {
		var lo = 0;
		var hi = 0;
		var gradeRange = $(".hiddenTDF").val();
		if (gradeRange) {
			lo = gradeRange.split("-")[0];
			hi = gradeRange.split("-")[1];
		}
		var subject = $("[id$=hiddenSubject]").prop("checked");
		var dateDesc = $("[id$=hiddenDateDesc]").prop("checked");
		return { "SC": CURRENT_SCHOOL_CODE, "SN": CURRENT_STUDENT_NUMBER, "LO": lo, "HI": hi, "Subject": subject, "DateDesc": dateDesc };
	};

	function GetStudentDistrictGPAs() {
		var cd = $("[id*=txtTDFValue]").val().replace("&nbsp;", "").trim();
		if ($(".stu-district-gpas").length) {
			$.ajax({
				type: "GET",
				url: "grades/gpa/student",
                data: { TranscriptCode: cd },
				cache: false,
                success: function (response) {
                    if (response) {
                        $(".stu-district-gpas").html("");
                        $(".stu-district-gpas").append(response);

                    }
                },
                error: function (error) {
                    aeriesWin.prototype.alert(error);
                }
			});
		}

	}

	function ToggleHIS_More(b) {

		if ($(b).closest("tr").next()) {
			if ($(b).closest("tr").next().is(":visible")) {
				$(b).closest("tr").next().hide();
				$(b).html('More');
			}
			else {
				$(b).closest("tr").next().show();
				$(b).html('Less');
			}
		}

		return false;
	}

	function btnSave_Click() {
		location.href = $('a[id*=SaveRcd]').attr('href');
	}

	function validateFloatKeyPress(el, evt) {
		var charCode = (evt.which) ? evt.which : event.keyCode;
		var number = el.value.split('.');
		if (charCode != 46 && charCode > 31 && (charCode < 48 || charCode > 57)) {
			return false;
		}
		//just one dot 
		if (number.length > 1 && charCode == 46) {
			return false;
		}
		//get the carat position
		var caratPos = getSelectionStart(el);
		var dotPos = el.value.indexOf(".");
		if (caratPos > dotPos && dotPos > -1 && (number[1].length > 1)) {
			return false;
		}
		return true;
	}

	function getSelectionStart(o) {
		if (o.createTextRange) {
			var r = document.selection.createRange().duplicate()
			r.moveEnd('character', o.value.length)
			if (r.text == '') return o.value.length
			return o.value.lastIndexOf(r.text)
		} else return o.selectionStart
	}

	function AMK_Change(ctrl) {
		var MarkAveragingGroup = $("input[id$='hdnMAG']").val();

		if (MarkAveragingGroup.length > 0) {
			if (confirm('Changing this value will reset the link, are you sure you want to change this value?')) {
				$("input[id$='hdnMAA']").val(true);
				SetMarkAveragingVisibility(true, false);
			} else {
				$(ctrl).val(prevValue);
			}
		}
	}

	function AverageMarks() {

		var MarksToAverage = new Array;
		var MarksTotalValue = 0;
		var MarkAverage = 0;
		var CourseMark = parseInt($('input[id$=txtMK]').val(), 10);

		$('.IncludeInMarkAverage input').each(function () {

			if ($(this).prop('checked')) {
				var mark = $(this).closest('tr').find('.AeriesMarkAverageSelector_Mark').text();
				MarksToAverage.push(mark);
			}

		});

		MarksToAverage.push(CourseMark);

		if (typeof MarksToAverage !== 'undefined' && MarksToAverage.length > 0) {
			for (var i = 0; i < MarksToAverage.length; i++) {
				MarksTotalValue += parseInt(MarksToAverage[i], 10);
			}
		}

		if (MarksTotalValue > 0) {
			MarkAverage = Math.round(MarksTotalValue / MarksToAverage.length);
		}

		$('input[id$=txtAMK]').val(MarkAverage);
		$("input[id$='hdnMAA']").val(false);

		setTimeout(function () {			
			MK_AfterUpdate($('input[id$=txtAMK]'));
		}, 100);
		
	}

	function OpenInlinePopup(popupControl) {

		if ($('#divMarkAveraging').hasClass('rolledup')) {
			var pos = $('#btnMarkAveragingLink').position();

			$('#divMarkAveraging').css('left', pos.left - $('#divMarkAveraging').width() + 13);
			$('#divMarkAveraging').css('top', pos.top + $('#btnMarkAveragingLink').height() + 7);
			$('#divMarkAveraging').removeClass('rolledup');
		} else {
			$('#divMarkAveraging').addClass('rolledup');
		}


	}

	function OpenMarkAveraging() {

		if ($('#divMarkAveraging').hasClass('rolledup')) {
			var pos = $('#btnMarkAveragingLink').position();

			$('#divMarkAveraging').css('left', pos.left - $('#divMarkAveraging').outerWidth() + $('#btnMarkAveragingLink').outerWidth());
			$('#divMarkAveraging').css('top', pos.top + $('#btnMarkAveragingLink').outerHeight());
			$('#divMarkAveraging').removeClass('rolledup');
		} else {
			$('#divMarkAveraging').addClass('rolledup');

	function SelectCN(e) {
		var CN = e.dataItem["CourseNumber"];
		$('input[id$=txtCN]').val(CN);
		$('input[id$=txtCN]').focus();
		$('#imgSearch').click();
		ChangeCNYR();

	function ChangeCNYR() {	

		var YR = $('select[id$=ddlYR]').val();
		var CN = $('input[id$=txtCN]').val();

		$('input[id$=hdnCN]').val(CN);		
		$('select[id$=hdnYR]').val(YR);		

		if (CN !== '') {
			PopulateCredits();
			PopulateCourseCharacteristics(CN);
		}

		$('input[id$=hdnIncludedSQs]').val('');

		if (SQ > 0) {
			setTimeout(function () {		
				$('[id$=btnRefreshEditControls]').click();  // this causes a post back, then closes the edit popup
				$('#divEditHIS-Loading').show();

			}, 100);

	function PopulateCourseCharacteristics(CN) {
        var webMethod = "transcripts/coursecharacteristics/getcoursecharacteristics/" + CN + "/";

        var request = $.ajax({
            url: webMethod,
            type: "GET",
            cache: false,
            dataType: "json"
        })
		request.done(function (result) {
			var characteristics = [];
			var kendoMultiSelect = null;

			if (result.length > 0) {
                var kendoMultiSelect = $("input[id$='txtCHC_txtControl']").data("kendoMultiSelect");				

                if (kendoMultiSelect) {
                    kendoMultiSelect.value(result);
					kendoMultiSelect.trigger("change");
				}
			}
        })
        request.fail(function (jqXHR, textStatus) {
            console.log("PopulateCourseCharacteristics failed: " + jqXHR.responseText);
        });
	}

	function PopulateCredits() {
		var CN = $('input[id$=txtCN]').val();
		GeneralFunctions.GetCourseInformation(CN, GetCourseInformation_Result);
	}

	function GetCourseInformation_Result(result) {
		if (result != null) {
			var $hdnCourseLevel = $('input[id$=hdnCRSCLEdit]');
			var $tdDualEnrollment = $('td[id$=tdEditRow51]');
			var $tdCollegeCreditHours = $('td[id$=tdEditRow52]');
			var $txtCollegeCreditHours = $('input[id$=txtCCH]');
			var CourseLevelResult = result[6].toString();
			var Credits = result[2].toFixed(2);

			$txtCollegeCreditHours.val('0.0000');
			$hdnCourseLevel.val(CourseLevelResult);

			if ($.inArray(CourseLevelResult, ['40', '23', '24']) > -1) {
				$tdDualEnrollment.show();
				$tdCollegeCreditHours.show();
			} else {
				$tdDualEnrollment.hide();
				$tdCollegeCreditHours.hide();
			}

			if (Credits > 0) {

				var $txtCreditAttempted = $('input[id$=txtCR]');
				var $txtCreditCompleted = $('input[id$=txtCC]');

				if (!IsNumeric($txtCreditAttempted.val()) || $txtCreditAttempted.val() == '') {
					$txtCreditAttempted.val(Credits);
					if ($txtCreditAttempted.is(':focus')) {
						$txtCreditAttempted.select();
					}
				}

                if ($('input[id*=txtABG]').val() != 'Y') {  // never update CC for Att Based Grd = 'Y'
                    if (!IsNumeric($txtCreditCompleted.val()) || $txtCreditCompleted.val() == '') {
                        $txtCreditCompleted.val(Credits);
                        if ($txtCreditCompleted.is(':focus')) {
                            $txtCreditCompleted.select();
                        }
                    }
                }

			}
		}
	}

	function MK_AfterUpdate(ctrl) {

		$MARK_CONTROL = $(ctrl);

		var MK = $(ctrl).val().toUpperCase();
		var SC = GetCurrentSchoolTaken();

		MARK = MK;
		GeneralFunctions.ValidMarkGRC(SC, MK, MK_AfterUpdateValid);
	}

	function MK_AfterUpdateValid(result) {

		var AverageMarkID = $MARK_CONTROL.attr('id').replace('txtMK', 'txtAMK');
		var MarkID = $MARK_CONTROL.attr('id').replace('txtAMK', 'txtMK');
		var MK = $('#' + MarkID).val().toUpperCase();

		$('#' + MarkID).val(MK)     // this appears to be what was intended, to make the mark uppercase

		var AMK = $('#' + AverageMarkID).val();

		var SC = GetCurrentSchoolTaken();

		if (typeof $MARK_CONTROL !== 'undefined' && $MARK_CONTROL.length > 0) {

			if (result == false) {
				ToggleEditPanelButtons(true)
				var myWin = new aeriesWin(winType.alert, 'Please enter a valid mark.');
				myWin.displayWin(SetFocusOnCtrl, $MARK_CONTROL);
				$MARK_CONTROL.val(prevMark);

			} else {
				
				var CreditsCompletedID = $MARK_CONTROL.attr('id').replace('txtMK', 'txtCC').replace('txtAMK', 'txtCC');
				var CreditsAttemptedID = $MARK_CONTROL.attr('id').replace('txtMK', 'txtCR').replace('txtAMK', 'txtCR');
				var $CreditsCompleted = $('#' + CreditsCompletedID);				
				var $CreditsAttempted = $('#' + CreditsAttemptedID);
				var CC = $CreditsCompleted.val();
				var CR = $CreditsAttempted.val();

				if (MK == 'X' || !IsNumeric(CC)) {
					$CreditsCompleted.val('0.00');
				}

				if (!IsNumeric(CR)) {
					$CreditsAttempted.val('0.00');
				}

				if (typeof AMK !== 'undefined' && AMK.length > 0) {
					if (MK < AMK) {
						MK = AMK;
						$MARK_CONTROL = $('input[id$=txtAMK]');
					}
				}

				GeneralFunctions.MK_AfterUpdate(SC, MK, CR, MK_AfterUpdate_Result);
			}
		}
	}

	function MK_AfterUpdate_Result(result) {

        var skipABG = false;    // only the "New" marks (Mass Add) do not have a related ABG - skip them
        if ($MARK_CONTROL.attr('id').indexOf("MKNew") >= 0) { skipABG = true; }

		var CreditsCompletedID = $MARK_CONTROL.attr('id').replace('txtMK', 'txtCC').replace('txtAMK', 'txtCC');
		var $CreditsCompleted = $('#' + CreditsCompletedID);
        var CC = result[1];

        if (IsNumeric(CC)) {
            if (skipABG || $('input[id*=txtABG]').val() != 'Y' ) {
                $CreditsCompleted.val(CC);
            }
		} 		

		SetMarkAveragingVisibility(true, false);

	}

	function Ctrl_AfterUpdate(ctrl) {
		var tmp = null;
		if ((ctrl.value * 1) > 0) {
			if (ctrl.value > 99) {
				if (!window.confirm('Are you sure you want a credit value of ' + ctrl.value + '?')) {
					ctrl.value = prevValue;
				}
			}
		}
	}

	function ToggleEditPanelButtons(disableControl) {
		let buttonControls = [
			$('[id*=btnSaveRcd]'),
			$('[id*=btnDeleteRcd]')
		]

		buttonControls.map( (ctrl) => {
			if(disableControl) {
				if (ctrl.prop('disabled') !== true) {
					ctrl.prop('disabled', true)
				}
			} else {
				if(ctrl.prop('disabled') === true) {
					ctrl.removeProp('disabled')
				}
			}
		})
	}

	function SetFocusOnCtrl(ctrl) {
		ToggleEditPanelButtons(false)
		$(ctrl).select().focus();
	}

	function GetCurrentSchoolTaken() {

		var SC;
		var $SchoolTaken = $('input[id$=txtST]');
		if ($SchoolTaken.length) {
			SC = $SchoolTaken.val();
		} else {
			SC = CURRENT_SCHOOL_CODE;
		}

		return SC;
	}

	function PopulateMarkAverageIncludedSQs() {

		var IncludedSQs = '';

		$('.IncludeInMarkAverage input').each(function () {
			if ($(this).prop('checked') === true) {
				if (IncludedSQs.length) {
					IncludedSQs += ',';

				IncludedSQs += GetMarkAveragingSQ($(this));
			}
		});

		$('input[id$=hdnIncludedSQs]').val(IncludedSQs);

		AverageMarks();
	}

	function IsRepeatTagValidForCredit(RT) {
		var RepeatTag = RT.trim().toUpperCase();
		var ValidForCredit = (RepeatTag == 'B' || RepeatTag == '3' || RepeatTag == '');
		return ValidForCredit;

		var MarkAveragingGroup = $('input[id$=hdnMarkAveragingGroup]').val();

		$('input[id$=chkIncludeInMarkAverage]').each(function () {
			var MAG = $('input[id$=hdnMAG]').val();

	function ConfirmMarkAverageChange(ctrl) {

		var MAG = $('input[id$=hdnMAG]').val();

		if (typeof MAG == 'undefined' || MAG == '') {
			PopulateMarkAverageIncludedSQs();

<script language="javascript" type="text/javascript">
		
    if (typeof (WebForm_FireDefaultButton) != 'undefined') {
        var origFireDefaultButton = WebForm_FireDefaultButton;
    }

    // override the default button event so we can stop ie
    // from triggering postback through non-intended,
    // implicit form submissions.
    WebForm_FireDefaultButton = function (event, target) {
        // only concerned about the enter key's odd behavior in ie
        if (event.keyCode == 13) {
            // srcElement is unique to ie.. other browsers support target
            var src = event.srcElement || event.target;

        	// don't call original function if focus is on a button which is not the default dummy button of the form 
			//*** 02/08/2016 HB -- the if statement below prevent all enter keys globally for all elements except inputs that are type submit or button. this prevents users from creating a newline in text areas (editors) 
            if ((src && (src.tagName.toLowerCase() == "input") && (src.type.toLowerCase() == "submit" || src.type.toLowerCase() == "button")) || (src && src.tagName.toLowerCase() == "textarea")) {
            	return true;
            } else {
            	return false;
            }
        }

        return origFireDefaultButton(event, target);
    }


	//Handles AJAX errors
	Sys.Application.add_load(AppLoad);

	//Sets the method to call to handle AJAX errors
	function AppLoad() {
		Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance().remove_endRequest(onEndRequest);
		Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance().add_endRequest(onEndRequest);
	}

	function onEndRequest(sender, args) {
		//Check to see if there's an error on this request
		if (args.get_error() != undefined) {
			var msg = args.get_error().message.replace("Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManagerServerErrorException: ", "");
			alert(msg);
			args.set_errorHandled(true);
		}
	}

	window.masterSC = $('.MasterSC').val();
	window.masterSN = $('.MasterSN').val();
	window.masterID = $('.MasterPID').val();

</script>

	<script type="text/javascript">
		// Keyup helper for fast typers
		var typingTimer;                //timer identifier
		var doneTypingInterval = 100;  //time in ms, 1/10th second

		function filterReportsKeyUp() {
			var searchText = $.trim($("#search-reports").val());
			if (searchText.length > 0) {
				filterReports(searchText);
			} else {
				resetReports();
			}
			HighlightFirstLink();
		}
		function filterNavKeyUp() {
			var searchText = $.trim($("#search-nav").val());
			if (searchText.length > 0) {
				filterSidebar(searchText);
			} else {
				resetSidebar(true);
				$(".sidebar-quick-access-icon-on.all-images").show();
			}
			HighlightFirstLink();
		}

		function sidebarViewUpdate() {
			var viewportWidth = $(window).width();
			if (viewportWidth < 991) {
				$("#wrapper").addClass("toggled");
				$(".menu-toggle").show();
				$(".sidebar-logo-a").show();
			}			
		}

		// hide sidebar nav when clicked outside of itself
		$(document).bind("mouseup touchend", function (e) {
			var container = $("#sidebar-wrapper");
			if (!container.is(e.target) && container.has(e.target).length === 0) {
				var viewportWidth = $(window).width();
				if (viewportWidth < 991) {
					var isToggled = $("#wrapper").hasClass("toggled");
					if (!isToggled) {
						$("#ul-sidebar-nav li a.menu-toggle").click();
					}
				}
			}
		});

		function getParameterByName(name, url) {
			if (!url) url = window.location.href;
			name = name.replace(/[\[\]]/g, "\\$&");
			var regex = new RegExp("[?&]" + name + "(=([^&#]*)|&|#|$)"),
				results = regex.exec(url);
			if (!results) return null;
			if (!results[2]) return '';
			return decodeURIComponent(results[2].replace(/\+/g, " "));
		}

		function setSidebarCssClasses() {
			// Set Reports as Selected class.
			if (window.location.href.indexOf("Reports.aspx") >= 0) {
				$("li.reports-root-link a[href$='Reports.aspx?cat=All']").closest("li.reports-root-link").addClass("Selected");
			}
			if (window.location.href.indexOf("RunReport.aspx?rptname=") >= 0) {
				var rptname = getParameterByName('rptname');
				if (rptname.length > 0) {
					$("li.reports-root-link a[href$='RunReport.aspx?rptname=" + rptname + "']").closest("li.reports-root-link").addClass("Selected");
					var categoryfound = $("li.reports-root-link.Selected").attr('cat');
					if (typeof categoryfound !== "undefined" && $("div[cat='" + categoryfound + "']").length > 0 && !$("div[cat='" + categoryfound + "']").hasClass("expanded")) {
						$("div[cat='" + categoryfound + "']").addClass("Selected");
						$("div[cat='" + categoryfound + "']").children("span").removeClass("icon-collapsed").addClass("icon-expanded");
						$("div[cat='" + categoryfound + "']").children("span").attr('title', 'Click to Collapse');
					}
				}
			}

			// parent 
			$("a.TreeNode:not(.LeafNode)").addClass("parent");

			// add angle icon to parent
			$("<span class='icon-collapsed pull-right parent-icon' title='Click to Expand'></span>").insertBefore(".parent");

			// parent wrapper
			$(".parent").closest("table").addClass("parent-wrapper Clickable");

			// sub parent
			$("a.TreeNode:not(.LeafNode, .RootTreeNode)").addClass("sub-parent");

			// child list wrapper
			$(".parent").closest("table").next("div").addClass("sidebar-child-list");

			// expand / collapse wrapper for sub parent
			$(".sub-parent").closest("tr").children("td:nth-child(2)").addClass("sub-expand-collapse-wrapper");

			// links
			$(".LeafNode").addClass("sidebar-link");

			// link wrapper
			$(".sidebar-link").closest("table").addClass("sidebar-link-wrapper Clickable zebra");

			// sidebar items
			$(".TreeView").children().addClass("sidebar-item");

			// favorite wrappers
			$(".TreeView").children().slice(1, 3).addClass("favs remove-from-sidebar-search").hide();

			// active side item
			var selectedList = $(".TreeNodeSelected").closest(".sidebar-child-list");
			selectedList.addClass("sidebar-item-active");
			$(".TreeNodeSelected").closest("table.sidebar-link-wrapper").addClass("selected-link-wrapper");
			$(".sidebar-item-active").prev("table.parent-wrapper").addClass("aeries-background-blue-light");
			$("table.parent-wrapper.aeries-background-blue-light").find("span.parent-icon").removeClass("icon-collapsed").addClass("icon-expanded");
			$("table.parent-wrapper.aeries-background-blue-light").find("span.parent-icon").attr('title', 'Click to Collapse');
			var isRootList = selectedList.hasClass("sidebar-item");
			if (isRootList == false) {
				$("table.parent-wrapper.aeries-background-blue-light").closest(".sidebar-child-list").prev("table.parent-wrapper").addClass("aeries-background-blue-light");
			}
			
			// student flags wrapper
			//$("div#NavTreeScroller > table > tbody > tr:first").addClass("student-flags-wrapper remove-from-sidebar-search");

			// Home button
			$(".TreeView > table:first").addClass("sidebar-home remove-from-sidebar-search");
			
			// Loop 
			$(".TreeView > table:nth-child(4)").addClass("sidebar-link-loop-wrapper");

			// TEMPORARY - KILL LOOP IMAGE
			var isLoop = $(".sidebar-link-loop-wrapper > tbody > tr > td:nth-child(2) > a:has(img)").length;
			if (isLoop) {
				$(".sidebar-link-loop-wrapper > tbody > tr > td:nth-child(2)").remove();
			}

			// Root link (No children)
			$("table.sidebar-item.sidebar-link-wrapper").addClass("sidebar-root-link-wrapper");

			// Flag wrapper
			$("img[src*='RedFlagSmall']").addClass("student-flag-image");
			$("table.sidebar-link-wrapper > tbody > tr td > a > img.student-flag-image").closest("table.sidebar-link-wrapper").addClass("student-flag-wrapper");

			// additional sidebar items
			$(".remove-from-sidebar-search").addClass("sidebar-item");
		}

		function setSidebarFilter() {

			var filterItem = localStorage.getItem("sidebarFilter");
			if (filterItem == "Favorites") {
				$("#favorites-submit").click();
			} else if (filterItem == "Flags") {
				$("#student-flag-submit").click();
			} else if (filterItem == "Reports") {
				$("#reports-submit").click();
			} else {
				setSidebarFilterStorage($("#all-pages-submit"));
			}
		}

		$("div.reports-category-title").click(function () {
			var $this = $(this);
			var isExpanded = $this.find("span.icon-expanded").length > 0;
			if (isExpanded == false) {
				$this.addClass("expanded");
				$this.children("span").removeClass("icon-collapsed").addClass("icon-expanded");
				$this.children("span").attr('title', 'Click to Collapse');
				$("li[cat='" + $this.attr('cat') + "']").not(".filtered").velocity("slideDown", { duration: 100 });
			} else {
				$this.removeClass("expanded");
				$this.removeClass("Selected");
				$this.children("span").removeClass("icon-expanded").addClass("icon-collapsed");
				$this.children("span").attr('title', 'Click to Expand');
				$("li[cat='" + $this.attr('cat') + "']").not(".filtered").velocity("slideUp", { duration: 150 });
			}			
		});

		$(".clear-all-filters").click(function () {
			$("#reset-search-nav:visible").click();
			$("#reset-search-reports:visible").click();
		});

		$("#reset-search-reports").click(function () {			
			resetReports();

		function KeyboardNavMove(direction) {

			var linkquery = 'td.TreeNode';
			if (FilterMode == 'reports') {
				linkquery = '.reports-root-link';
			}

			var TotalNumberOfLinks = $(linkquery + ':visible').length;
			var CurrentPositionOfLink = 0;
			var NextPositionOfLink = 0;

			if (TotalNumberOfLinks >= 1) {
				// Get Current Position of Highlight.
				var templinkposition = 0;
				$(linkquery + ':visible').each(function () {
					if ($(this).hasClass('NavHighlighted')) {
						CurrentPositionOfLink = templinkposition;
					}
					templinkposition = templinkposition + 1;
				});

				if (direction == 'up') {
					if ($(linkquery + '.NavHighlighted:visible').length >= 1) {
						// Go up from currently selected item.
						NextPositionOfLink = CurrentPositionOfLink - 1;
						if (NextPositionOfLink <= -1) {
							NextPositionOfLink = (TotalNumberOfLinks - 1);
						}
						$(linkquery + '.NavHighlighted').removeClass('NavHighlighted');
						$(linkquery + ':visible').eq(NextPositionOfLink).addClass('NavHighlighted');
					} else {
						// First time pressing up. find the first item.
						$('a.sidebar-link:visible').last().closest(linkquery + ':visible').addClass('NavHighlighted');
					}
				} else if(direction == 'down') {
					if ($(linkquery + '.NavHighlighted:visible').length >= 1) {
						// Go up from currently selected item.
						NextPositionOfLink = CurrentPositionOfLink + 1;
						if (NextPositionOfLink >= TotalNumberOfLinks) {
							NextPositionOfLink = 0;
						}
						$(linkquery + '.NavHighlighted').removeClass('NavHighlighted');
						$(linkquery + ':visible').eq(NextPositionOfLink).addClass('NavHighlighted');
					} else {
						HighlightFirstLink();
					}
				}
				ScrollNavToHighlight();
				HighlightLink();
			}			
		}

		function HighlightLink() {

			var linkquery = 'td.TreeNode';
			if (FilterMode == 'reports') {
				linkquery = '.reports-root-link';
			}

			try {
				$('.keyboard-selected-link-wrapper:visible').removeClass('keyboard-selected-link-wrapper');
				$(linkquery + '.NavHighlighted:visible').closest('table').addClass('keyboard-selected-link-wrapper');
			} catch (ex) {
			}			
		}

		function HighlightFirstLink() {

			// First time pressing up. find the first item.
			$('.NavHighlighted').removeClass('NavHighlighted');
			
			if (FilterMode == 'reports') {
				$('.reports-root-link:visible').first().addClass('NavHighlighted');				
			} else {
				$('a.sidebar-link:visible').first().closest('td.TreeNode:visible').addClass('NavHighlighted');
			}
			HighlightLink();
		}

		var FilterMode = 'nav';

		// Look for Up, Down, and Enter while filtering the nav.
		$('body').on('keydown', function (e) {

			// Check if filter is focued.
			var isFocused = false;
			try {
				isFocused = $('.quick-search-input:visible').is(':focus');
			} catch (ex) {
			}
			
			// Skip if there are no links in nav, or if filter is not focused...
			if ( ($('a.sidebar-link:visible').length + $('.reports-root-link:visible').length) <= 0 || !isFocused) { return; }

			if ($('.quick-search-input:visible').attr('id') == 'search-reports') {
				FilterMode = 'reports';
			} else {				
				FilterMode = 'nav';
			}

			switch (e.which) {
				case 38: // up
					KeyboardNavMove('up');
					break;

				case 40: // down
					KeyboardNavMove('down');
					break;

				case 13: // enter

					var alinkhref = '';
					try {
						if (FilterMode == 'reports') {
							alinkhref = $('li.NavHighlighted:visible a').eq(0).attr('href');
						} else {
							alinkhref = $('td.NavHighlighted:visible a.TreeNode').eq(0).attr('href');
						}						
					} catch (ex) {}

					if ( ($('td.NavHighlighted:visible a.TreeNode').length + $('li.NavHighlighted:visible a').length) >= 1 && alinkhref != '') {
						if (alinkhref.indexOf('javascript:') >= 0) {
							eval(alinkhref.replace('javascript:', ''));
						} else {
							window.location = alinkhref;
						}						
					} else {
						return;
					}
					break;

				default: return; // exit this handler for other keys
			}
			e.preventDefault(); // prevent the default action (scroll / move caret)
		});

		function AddContactLine(ContactInfoType, ContactData, FieldName) {
			var iconName = "users";
			if (ContactInfoType == 'Telephone') {
				iconName = "phone";
				// Transform Phone Number
				ContactData = ContactData.replace(/(\d{3})(\d{3})(\d{4})/, '($1) $2-$3');
			} else if (ContactInfoType == 'Address') {
				iconName = "map-marker";
			} else if (ContactInfoType == 'Email') {
				iconName = "envelope";
			}

			var sectionTitle = "Contact Information";
			if ($(".reverse-lookup-input[value='" + ContactInfoType + "']").length > 0) {
				sectionTitle = $(".reverse-lookup-input[value='" + ContactInfoType + "']").closest("label").attr('title');
			}
			if (typeof FieldName != "undefined" && FieldName.length > 0) {
				sectionTitle = FieldName;
			}

			return "<span title='" + sectionTitle + "'><i class='fa fa-" + iconName + "' aria-hidden='true'></i> " + ContactData + "</span>";
		}

		function BuildContactListDetails(contactListDiv, searchString, reverseSearchType) {
			if (contactListDiv.find("contactlist").length > 0) {
				var fullHTMLContactList = "";				
				var isFound = 0;
				contactListDiv.find("contactlist").each(function () {
					var htmlContactList = "";
					var isContactFound = 0;
					var contactObject = $(this);
					var contactname = contactObject.attr("nm");
					if (contactname.length <= 2) { contactname = contactObject.attr("fn") + " " + contactObject.attr("ln"); }

					// By Section Show only matching data, hide contacts and data that does not match.
					if (reverseSearchType == "Telephone") {										
						TelephoneList.split(", ").forEach(function (entry) {
							var lookupEntry = entry.toLowerCase().replace("stu.","").replace("con.","");
							if (entry.indexOf("CON") !== -1 && StringHas(contactObject.attr(lookupEntry), searchString.replace(/[^0-9\.]/g, ''))) {
								htmlContactList += AddContactLine(reverseSearchType, contactObject.attr(lookupEntry), entry);
								isContactFound = 1;
							}
						});
					}
					if (reverseSearchType == "Address") {
						AddressList.split(", ").forEach(function (entry) {
							var lookupEntry = entry.toLowerCase().replace("stu.", "").replace("con.", "");
							if (entry.indexOf("CON") !== -1 && StringHas(contactObject.attr(lookupEntry), searchString)) {
								htmlContactList += AddContactLine(reverseSearchType, contactObject.attr(lookupEntry), entry);
								isContactFound = 1;
							}
						});
					}
					if (reverseSearchType == "Email") {
						EmailList.split(", ").forEach(function (entry) {
							var lookupEntry = entry.toLowerCase().replace("stu.", "").replace("con.", "");
							if (entry.indexOf("CON") !== -1 && StringHas(contactObject.attr(lookupEntry), searchString)) {
								htmlContactList += AddContactLine(reverseSearchType, contactObject.attr(lookupEntry), entry);
								isContactFound = 1;
							}
						});
					}
					if (reverseSearchType == "Contact") {
						if (StringHas(contactname, searchString)) {
							isContactFound = 1;
						}
					}
					if (isContactFound == 1) {
						htmlContactList = AddContactLine("Contact", contactname, ContactList.replace("STU.PG, ","")) + htmlContactList;
						isFound = 1;						
						fullHTMLContactList += htmlContactList;
					}
				});
				
				contactListDiv.html(fullHTMLContactList);
				if (isFound == 1) {					
					contactListDiv.show();
				}
			}
		}

		function studentResultsLoaded() {
			// Place Cursor in search box
			CursorInput($(".student-search-pop-input"));
			var searchString = $("input.student-search-pop-input").val();
			var reverseSearchType = $("input[id$='_StuSearchReverseFilter']").val();

			// Show any Reverse Searches
			if (reverseSearchType.length > 1 && $(".filter-tag.deleteme").length <= 0) {
				try {
					$(".reverse-lookup-input[value='" + reverseSearchType + "']").click();
					showCurrentFilters();
				} catch (Err) {
				}
			}

			// Reset View			
			resetStudentResults();

			// Are we skipping students?
			if ($(".reset-skip-button").length > 0 || $("#divKeepSkipTemp:visible").length > 0) {
				$(".skip-actions").show();
			}

			// Update Row Count
			var results = 0;
			if ($(".StuSearchResultsTable .zebra").length >= 1) {
				results = $(".StuSearchResultsTable .zebra").length;
			}
			$("#StuSearchRowCount").html("<span>" + results + "</span> Results");

			

			// Hide Loading screen
			$("#StuSearchPlaceholder-Loading").hide();

			// Show Placeholder if no results found
			if (results == 0) {
				$("#StuSearchPlaceholder").show();
				$("#KeepStudents").hide();
				if ($(".student-search-pop-input").val().length >= 1) {
					$("#StuSearchPlaceholder-Welcome").hide();
					$("#StuSearchPlaceholder-NoResults").show();
				} else {
					$("#StuSearchPlaceholder-NoResults").hide();
					$("#StuSearchPlaceholder-Welcome").show();
					$("#StuSearchRowCount").html("<span></span>");
					$("#KeepStudents").hide();
				}
			} else {
				// Only show Keep Students option if not searching all schools
				try {
					UserAccountOptionsService.GetOption("SearchAllSchools", function (result) {
						if (result !== 'True') {
							$("#KeepStudents").show();
						}
					});
				} catch (err) {
					$("#KeepStudents").show();
				}
				// Find and apply any contact level detail results
				$(".contact-list").each(function () {
					BuildContactListDetails($(this), searchString, reverseSearchType);
				});

				MakeTableSortable($(".StuSearchResultsTable"));

				// load only images in the viewport
				LazyLoadStuPic();
			}
		}

				maskedtext.destroy();
			} catch (Err) { }

			// Add Masks if needed.
			if ($(this).val() == "Telephone") {
				$("input[id$='_StuSearchValue']").kendoMaskedTextBox({ mask: "(999) 000-0000" });
			} else if ($(this).val() == "DOB") {
				$("input[id$='_StuSearchValue']").kendoMaskedTextBox({ mask: "00/00/0000" });
			}
			CursorInput($(".student-search-pop-input"));
		});

		// Clear reverse lookup
		$('body').on('click touchstart', '#reverse-lookup-option-clear', function () {
			$(".reverse-lookup-input").closest(".tag.activated").removeClass("activated");
			$(".student-search-pop-input").val("");
			$('.reverse-lookup-input').prop('checked', false);
			$(".student-search-pop-input").attr("placeholder", "Search students...");
			$("input[id$='_StuSearchReverseFilter']").val("");
			closeFilter("#reverse-lookup");
			var datepicker = $("input[id$='_StuSearchValue']").data("kendoDatePicker");
			try {
				datepicker.destroy();
			} catch (Err) { }
			var maskedtext = $("input[id$='_StuSearchValue']").data("kendoMaskedTextBox");
			try {
				maskedtext.destroy();
			} catch (Err) { }
			CursorInput($(".student-search-pop-input"));
		});
		$('body').on('click touchstart', '.clearreverse', function () {
			$('#reverse-lookup-option-clear').click();
		});

		// Show Advanced Search Filters
		$('body').on('click', '#advanced-search', function () {
			$("#reverse-lookup-filters").hide();
			// Is it expanded?
			if ($("#advanced-search").find("span").hasClass("icon-expanded")) {
				$("#advanced-search").find("span").removeClass("icon-expanded").addClass("icon-collapsed");
				$("#advanced-search").find("span").attr('title', 'Click to Expand');
				$("#advanced-search-filters").velocity("slideUp", { duration: 250 });
			} else {
				$("#advanced-search").find("span").removeClass("icon-collapsed").addClass("icon-expanded");
				$("#advanced-search").find("span").attr('title', 'Click to Collapse');
				$("#advanced-search-filters").velocity("slideDown", {
					duration: 250
				});
			}
		});

		// Search buttons - Prevent Multi Clicks
		$('body').on('click', '.clickonce', function () {			
			$('.clickonce').attr("disabled", true);
			$("#StuSearchPlaceholder-Loading").show();			
			resetStudentResults();
		});

		$('body').on('click', '.reset-skip', function () {
			$(".reset-skip-button").click();
			try {
				$(".reset-skip-button-temp").click();
			} catch (ex) {

			}
		});

		// At the end of any built-in .net ajax calls...
		Sys.WebForms.PageRequestManager.getInstance().add_endRequest(function (sender, e) {
			try {
				if (sender._activeElement.id.indexOf("btnSearch") >= 0 || sender._activeElement.id.indexOf("btnStuSearchGo") >= 0 || sender._activeElement.id.indexOf("btnGroupSearchGo") >= 0 || sender._activeElement.id.indexOf("last10-students-link") >= 0) {
					// Clear out search, list all function should be explicitly understood
					if (sender._activeElement.id.indexOf("btnGroupSearchGo") >= 0) {
						$(".student-search-pop-input").val("");
					}
					studentResultsLoaded();
				} else {
					AddTitlesToImages();
				}
			} catch (err) {
			}
		});

		function StuSearch() {
			var searchInput = $('.search-input').val();			
			if (searchInput.length > 0) {
				$('.student-search-pop-input').val(searchInput);
				SubmitStudentSearch();
				// Reset Search Input				
				$('.search-input').val("");
			} else {
				studentResultsLoaded();
			}

			// Open Kendo Window
			setTimeout(function () {
				$(".StudentSearchModal").data("kendoWindow").open().center();
			}, 0);
		}
	
		$("#favorites-submit").click(function () {
			$("#reset-search-nav").click();
			$("#reset-search-nav:visible").click();
			$(".sidebar-quick-access-icon-filtered").hide();
			$("#search-nav-wrapper").hide();
			$("#search-reports-wrapper").hide();

			// Hide Other Sections
			$("#sidebar-reports").hide();			
			$(".sidebar-item").hide();

			// Show Favorites
			$("#sidebar-pages").show();
			$(".favs").velocity("fadeIn", { duration: 150 });

			setSidebarFilterStorage($(this));
			$("#sidebar-content").slimScroll({ scrollTo: "0px" });
		});

		$("#student-flag-submit").click(function () {
			$("#sidebar-reports").hide();
			$("#sidebar-pages").show();
			$("#search-nav-wrapper").hide();
			resetSidebar();
			$(".sidebar-child-list").show();
			$(".remove-from-sidebar-search").hide().addClass("filtered");
			$(".sidebar-link-wrapper:not(.student-flag-wrapper)").hide().addClass("filtered");
			$(".sidebar-link-wrapper.student-flag-wrapper").show().removeClass("filtered");
			hideParentlessBranch();

			setSidebarFilterStorage($(this));
		});

		$("#all-pages-submit").click(function () {			
			$("#search-reports-wrapper").hide();
			$("#search-nav-wrapper").show();

			$("#sidebar-reports").hide();
			$("#sidebar-pages").show();	
			CursorInput($("#search-nav"));
			$(".sidebar-item").show();
			resetSidebar();			
			setSidebarFilterStorage($(this));
			NavScrolled = false;
			setTimeout(function () {
				ScrollNav();
			}, 400);
		});

		$("#reports-submit").click(function () {
			$("#search-nav-wrapper").hide();
			$("#search-reports-wrapper").show();
			$(".sidebar-quick-access-icon-filtered").hide();
			$(".sidebar-quick-access-icon-off").show();
			$("#sidebar-pages").hide();
			$("#sidebar-reports").show();
			if (window.location.href.toLowerCase().indexOf('query.aspx') == -1) { CursorInput($("#search-reports")); }
			setSidebarFilterStorage($(this));
			resetReports();
			NavScrolled = false;
			setTimeout(function () {
				ScrollNav();
			}, 400);
		});

		function setSidebarFilterStorage(filterWrapper) {
			if ($("#search-nav").val().length > 0) {
				$("#search-nav").val('')
			}

			$(".sidebar-quick-access-wrapper-on").removeClass("sidebar-quick-access-wrapper-on");
			$(".sidebar-quick-access-icon-on").hide();
			$(".sidebar-quick-access-icon-off").show();
			var text = filterWrapper.children(".sidebar-quick-access-text").text();
			filterWrapper.children(".sidebar-quick-access-icon-off").hide();
			filterWrapper.children(".sidebar-quick-access-icon-on").show();
			filterWrapper.addClass("sidebar-quick-access-wrapper-on");
			localStorage.setItem("sidebarFilter", text);
		}
						
		// Overrides jQuery's :contains removing case sensitivity
		$.expr[":"].contains = $.expr.createPseudo(function (arg) {
			return function (elem) {
				return $(elem).text().toUpperCase().indexOf(arg.toUpperCase()) >= 0;
			};
		});

		$("#favorite-submit").click(function () {
			var popupNotification = $("#popupNotification").kendoNotification().data("kendoNotification");
			var isFavorite = $("#favorite-submit .fa-star").length > 0;
			if (isFavorite == true) {
				RemoveFavorite();
				$("#favorite-submit .fa-star").removeClass("fa-star aeries-yellow").addClass("fa-star-o");
			} else {
				AddFavorite();
				$("#favorite-submit .fa-star-o").removeClass("fa-star-o").addClass("fa-star aeries-yellow");
			}
		});


		function SetStudentSearchLimiter(dropdownElement) {
			GeneralFunctions.SetSearchResultLimit(dropdownElement.value);
		}
	</script>



</body>
</html>
